Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}特警屠龙 {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}动作快一点{\r}\NFaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拿一包给我{\r}\NGive me a bag
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大哥{\r}\NBig Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}正货，果然是实力派{\r}\NThe real thing, so it's lived up its name
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海洛英，你要多少有多少{\r}\NHeroine can be had in any quantity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听说你在纽约很吃得开，一起做过江龙{\r}\NThey say you've a way in NY. Let's combine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}将美国的海洛英市场全部捉过来{\r}\Nto snatch your heroine businesses from them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，有钱大家赚{\r}\NOkay, it's mutually beneficial
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在我要二十公斤货{\r}\NNow I want 20 kilos of that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}钱呢{\r}\NWhere's the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在这里{\r}\NHere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别说我不把你教得聪明一点{\r}\NMind you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有一哥在这里，千万别乱说话{\r}\NDon't talk nonsense in front of Mr. Big Brother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}敢向我拔枪，你想找死？{\r}\NTrying to draw? Are you looking for hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有种{\r}\NGreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我跟你合作，其他家族一定没生意可做{\r}\NIf you work with me, the other families will go bust
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小熊是我的亲兄弟，拿二十公斤货来{\r}\NHe's my brother. Get 20 kgs of stuff for him
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这个死仔炳{\r}\NYou bustard Ping!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不许动，警察{\r}\NDon't move, CID!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不许动{\r}\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不许动，警察，把枪放下{\r}\NDon't move! Police, drop your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}该死的{\r}\NDamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把枪放下{\r}\NDrop your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大哥，快跑{\r}\NBig brother, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别动{\r}\NStay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把枪放下，慢慢起来{\r}\NDrop your gun and climb up slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别想着耍花样，老子的枪很容易走火{\r}\NNo monkey business! My gun has no eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}双手拉着自己的耳朵{\r}\NPut your hands on your ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老子出马，从不失手{\r}\NI never flop in any mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你妈的{\r}\NDamn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没事吧？德叔{\r}\NAre you alright, Uncle Te?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没事{\r}\NYes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么会老猫烧须？{\r}\NWell, an experienced fireman gets his fingers hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}多事{\r}\NNonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还想跑？{\r}\NTrying to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走开{\r}\NGet out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要跑，警察{\r}\NStop, police
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别动...{\r}\NFreeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别乱来{\r}\NKeep away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点把枪放下，还不放下我就打死她{\r}\NDrop your gun! Drop or I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把枪放下，听到了没有？{\r}\NCome on, put it down! Hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}否则我开枪打死她，快放下{\r}\NDrop it or I'll shoot her dead
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快放下{\r}\NDrop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}岂有此理，你这个死家伙{\r}\NOutrageous! You scum
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这个家伙，想找死？{\r}\NAre you sick of living?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}全部蹲下{\r}\NKeep down, police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这个家伙，不想活了？{\r}\NAre you fed up with living?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}追{\r}\NAfter him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉，不要上来，危险{\r}\NShirley, don't come up! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}叫蛙人来打捞{\r}\NGet the frogmen to salvage
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}刚才你不要命了吗？{\r}\NDid you mean to get killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起{\r}\NSorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官{\r}\NMr.Huang
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}马上封锁现场，叫救伤车来{\r}\NCordon off the spot and call an ambulance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官...{\r}\NMr.Huang...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大家辛苦了{\r}\NThank you all for the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}差一点忘了哪里去找回一条鱼饵给莎莉{\r}\NI nearly forgot to get back a bait for Shirley
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}德叔，看看找到了多少毒品{\r}\NUncle Te, see how much our haul is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}修哥，你的眼镜修好了再还给你{\r}\NHsiu, here you are, fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好{\r}\NGood
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}韦长官{\r}\NMr.Wei
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}美国有一个档案来了{\r}\NHere's a file from the USA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一班是美国新兴的贩毒集团{\r}\NThis new drug syndicate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在来了香港{\r}\Nis now in HK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你留心一下他们的动静{\r}\NWatch their movements
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:10:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}多喝一杯庆祝一下{\r}\NLet's have more
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.46,0:11:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}已经喝了很多了{\r}\NI've had enough
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}干杯...{\r}\NCheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要... 什么不要{\r}\NDon't... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真的不能喝{\r}\NReally can't drink
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你骗人，不能喝{\r}\NYou're lying
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了...{\r}\NEnough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那我明天才多喝一杯{\r}\NWell, I'll drink more tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明天再算{\r}\NLet's talk about it tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}事先声明{\r}\NListen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明天谁敢乱来就把他调到沙头角去{\r}\Nanyone making trouble tomorrow will be transferred to Shataukok
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这不是公报私仇吗？{\r}\NAre you trying to avenge a personal grudge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么公报私仇？{\r}\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官，你来评评道理{\r}\NMr.Huang judge for us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们当他是朋友才替他庆祝一下{\r}\NWe celebrated for him because we took him for a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他现在不当我们是朋友，你有什么看法{\r}\NHe's not taking us for friends. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你要帮帮我，要不然我醉定了{\r}\NHelp me, or I'll get drunk for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}行{\r}\NOkay
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明天你结婚，如果你不跟我喝这一杯{\r}\NYou're getting married tomorrow. Drink this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉就要替我收拾房子{\r}\Nor Shirley has to clean the house for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对，莎莉要一个人留下来拾垃圾{\r}\NRight, Shirley will stay to clear up the rubbish
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你以为做家庭主妇那么容易{\r}\NDon't think it's easy to be a housewife
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那你想不想他喝，我是不大想{\r}\NDo you want him to drink. I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么样？  喝了它{\r}\NWell? Drink it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要喝{\r}\NDon't drink
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喝这么大杯{\r}\NDrink this big glass
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还没有过门就公然维护着他{\r}\NDon't side with him so soon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看见你们俩这么恩爱{\r}\NWe bachelors...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真是令我们这一班王老五羡慕了{\r}\Nreally envy your true feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你就开心了，明天就离开我们不干{\r}\NYou're Iucky, you're quitting tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不过手足们就真的不开心了{\r}\NBut we really are depressed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还搏什么？昨天医生才说过我的心脏不好{\r}\NWhy fight? Only yesterday the doctor said my heart's weak
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么？{\r}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}受不了刺激{\r}\NI can't stand the shock
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有时候医生的话用不着全相信的{\r}\NSometimes you can't take a doctor advice too serious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}师姐，修哥受不了刺激，你受得{\r}\NSister, he can't stand the shock. Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一杯不喝也一样要留下来收拾房子{\r}\NYou don't drink this, you must clean the house
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你去执骨好了{\r}\NGo and collect the ashes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}斗酒伤身不好的，不如斗气好吗？{\r}\NDrinking's bad for health. What about venting our feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}更对胃口，我是处男{\r}\NThat suits me better. I'm a virgin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}反正蹩了一肚子气，来，斗吧{\r}\NI've lots of grievances, lets vent them
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，过来{\r}\NAh Yu, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事，修哥？  你是怎么搞的？{\r}\NWhat's it, Hsiu? What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}替我摆平他{\r}\NFix him for me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}修哥，这个是命令还是私人感情？{\r}\NIs that an order or a friendly request?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是自己人才叫你这么做{\r}\NOnly a friend would tell you to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个游戏规则不准看，下颚不准动{\r}\NNo peeping and no moving of lowerjaws
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}鸡蛋吹到对方那一边就算赢{\r}\NAnyone blowing the egg to an opponent win
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}准备{\r}\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}准备{\r}\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开始{\r}\NStart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}修哥，我帮你，你还耍我？{\r}\NHsiu, I'm on your side. Why tease me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天不玩就再没有机会玩了{\r}\NEither we play today or never
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.18,0:13:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}玩？就算你是我师父，我也要耍你一次{\r}\NEven if you were my master, I'd tease you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爱美...{\r}\NAmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好厉害{\r}\NTerrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}整我？{\r}\NMake fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要玩了，爱美真的来了{\r}\NStop that. Amy really is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我才不管呢 真的来了{\r}\NI don't care about her. She really is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来了又怎么样？{\r}\NSo what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不管我什么？{\r}\NIt's you who don't care about me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没什么{\r}\NEverything alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爱美 什么？{\r}\NAmy. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}连我的女朋友你也敢耍{\r}\NHow dare you lay hands on my girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}师姐保护我 不要玩了...{\r}\NProtect me. Stop fooling around
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}算了吧{\r}\NForget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}岂有此理{\r}\NOutrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去死吧{\r}\NBastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这个死家伙，来真的{\r}\NHow dare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁敢耍爱美我就要他好看{\r}\NAnyone teasing Amy will get it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}玩出火了...{\r}\NHe's flaring up
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你怎么了？{\r}\NWhat's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没事{\r}\NIt's alright
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们都是这么疯的，别理他们，烧东西吃{\r}\NThey're always so wild. Never mind them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官，挡着他{\r}\NMr.Huang, stop him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你两个家伙又玩什么新花样？{\r}\NWhat's you up to again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个臭小子打我{\r}\NThat bastard hit me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好心你们别玩得这么疯{\r}\NDon't go so wild, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}报告黄长官，现在是观乐时光{\r}\NMr.Huang, now is the Happy Hour
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.86,0:14:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就算是干妈下命令，我们也一于照玩{\r}\NWe'll go on even if Madam ordered us to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你两个马骝连我也敢耍{\r}\NDare you even to tease me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起，长官{\r}\NSorry, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.98,0:14:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们下水陪你{\r}\NWe'll go down to accompany you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来得好，敢把我扔下来{\r}\NGood, you dared to fling me down
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}进来吧{\r}\NCome in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}喝得我全身发烫{\r}\NIt really got into my head
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}给我弄杯咖啡解解酒{\r}\NGet me a cup of coffee, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}麻烦你{\r}\NThank you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}送给我的吗？{\r}\NFor me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}本来我是想拿来送给莎莉的{\r}\NI planned to give it to Shirley
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不过现在想起来还是你合用一点{\r}\NNow I think it suits you better
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就要看看{\r}\NIt depends
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这东西怎么会合我用？{\r}\NHow could it suit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天晚上你就不合用{\r}\NNot for tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不过从明天开始，就要疼爱莎莉{\r}\NAs of tomorrow, you need to love Shirley
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}做她的佣人{\r}\Nyou're to work like a slave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上一次整我{\r}\NYou tease me last time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，让我给你享用一点催泪气体{\r}\NWell have some tear-gas
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好让你结婚也哭个饱{\r}\NSo you'll cry on your wedding day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不是这么夸张吧？{\r}\NDon't exaggerate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真是服了你{\r}\NOkay, you win
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让开{\r}\NMake way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}让我来{\r}\NLet me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不用，笨手笨脚{\r}\NNo, you're cIumsy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就最好了{\r}\NSo much the better
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，先享受一杯咖啡{\r}\NLet me taste this nice cup of coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你心脏不好，以后不准喝咖啡{\r}\NYour heart's weak. Don't drink coffee anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么你当真的？我是骗他们的{\r}\NI only meant to fool them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那你连我也骗了？{\r}\NYou've fooled me too
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是...{\r}\NNo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不准骗，快点老老实实说{\r}\NStop lying, tell me the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是不是喜欢莎莉？{\r}\NDo you love Shirley?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不肯说就是不喜欢了{\r}\NIf you don't say it, it means you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不是，不过...{\r}\NNo, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不过想了这么久就是还没有决定{\r}\NI still can't make up my mind after such a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那我喜欢好了{\r}\NI love her then
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说得这么随便，就是没有诚意{\r}\NYou're not sincere
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}讲完了没有？{\r}\NHave you finished talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}催你了，走吧{\r}\NGo now, They're pushing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那我走了{\r}\NI'll go then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拜拜...{\r}\NBye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真没心肝，笨蛋...{\r}\NReally heartless, idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}先脱了它{\r}\NTake it off first
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是{\r}\NRight
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}记着明天早上十点我来接新娘{\r}\NRemember to collect the bride at 10 tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}结一条领带{\r}\NWear a necktie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢，拜拜{\r}\NThank you. Bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点来试一试{\r}\NTry it at once
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真漂亮{\r}\NReally beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}头花很好看{\r}\NThe flower on the head is beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}修哥{\r}\NHsiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别跑{\r}\NDon't run
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}修哥{\r}\NHsiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点叫救伤车{\r}\NCall an ambulance at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}修哥{\r}\NHsiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎...莎莉，我...{\r}\NShir..Shirley, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}修哥...{\r}\NHsiu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}发生什么事？{\r}\NWhat happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}警察{\r}\NC.I.D
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}全人类的天父{\r}\NHeavenly Father of all men
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们特为所爱而以后不能再见的人{\r}\NWe pray especially for those we love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.66,0:21:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}向主祷告{\r}\Nbut can't see any more
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.26,0:21:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}求主赐平安予他们，以永恒之光照临他们{\r}\NMay you bless them and shine on them
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在主的慈爱、智慧及全能权柄当中{\r}\NMay the love, wisdom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}愿天父的完全旨意{\r}\Nand omnipotence
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}所有的良善目的能在他们身上献上{\r}\Nbe demonstrated in them
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}此乃我主耶稣基督要求，阿门{\r}\NWe pray in Jesus' name, Amen
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你正在休假，你干么还回来？{\r}\NWhy are you back from your leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在休假也没意义{\r}\NThere's no point in taking leave now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}米高，我想申请销假{\r}\NMichael, I'm applying for return to duty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也好，有事情做对你会好一点{\r}\NGood. Work may do you good
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}八爷，我真的有麻烦，你要帮我一下{\r}\NMaster. I'm in trouble. You must help
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这个家伙，搞到这么严重{\r}\NYou made things so bad
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}手足们怎么肯帮你{\r}\NWho'd help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.86,0:23:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这样吧，这里有一服花旗参{\r}\NHere's a potion of American ginseng
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看它能不能够帮到你{\r}\NSee if it will help
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要动，警察{\r}\NDon't move. Police
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，把他铐上{\r}\NYu, handcuff him
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要动{\r}\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}潮洲雄在什么地方？{\r}\NWhere's Swatow Hsiung?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不知道，大姐{\r}\NI don't know. Miss
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.10,0:24:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不知道...{\r}\NI don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.46,0:24:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说{\r}\NSpeak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真的不知道{\r}\NI really don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.70,0:24:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你跟他是好兄弟，怎么会不知道？讲{\r}\NYou're his best friend! Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.70,0:24:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}讲{\r}\NSpeak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.66,0:24:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看你讲不讲{\r}\NAre you going to speak or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.34,0:24:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，他不肯讲，说不定这两个怪兽会讲{\r}\NMaybe these 2 monsters may speak
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.54,0:24:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要，我什么都不知道{\r}\NSorry, I don't know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.98,0:24:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走{\r}\NLet's go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.22,0:24:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要，老大{\r}\NDon't, Mr.Big
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.10,0:24:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}到那边去{\r}\NGo over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.46,0:24:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要吓倒我的女上司{\r}\NDon't scare madam
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.26,0:24:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们两个聪明的就快点讲{\r}\NBe smart and speak
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.82,0:24:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真的不知道{\r}\NI really don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.78,0:24:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果不肯讲的话，烫焦了屁股我可不负责{\r}\NDon't blame me if your bottom gets burnt
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.66,0:24:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}听到了没有？{\r}\NHear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.82,0:24:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真的不知道{\r}\NI really don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.06,0:24:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么了？不讲是吗？讲{\r}\NWell, are you going to speak or not. Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.26,0:25:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}脱裤子{\r}\NTake off your pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.54,0:25:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}脱裤子{\r}\NTake off your pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.18,0:25:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不讲是吗？烫他{\r}\NYou're not speaking? Scald him
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.18,0:25:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了{\r}\NGood
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.02,0:25:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我最喜欢烫屁股{\r}\NI enjoy doing it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.02,0:25:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}岂有此理，敢不把老子放在眼内{\r}\NYou don't care a damn about me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还不快讲？讲不讲？{\r}\NSpeak up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.14,0:25:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还不讲...{\r}\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还不讲...{\r}\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.62,0:25:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}昏过了去了{\r}\NHe's collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.06,0:25:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当然了，屁股给烫焦了{\r}\NHis bottom's got burnt
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.42,0:25:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}外面那一个可能熬得住{\r}\NThat one outside may last longer
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.18,0:25:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，烫他 拿来{\r}\NOkay, scald him. Give it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.58,0:25:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}脱裤子{\r}\NTake off your pants
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.74,0:25:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我讲...我只知道他明天坐船逃亡{\r}\NI'll speak... I only know he's sailing tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.22,0:25:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}在什么地方我就不知道，我就知道这么多{\r}\Nbut I don't know where
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.50,0:25:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要过来...{\r}\NKeep away...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.46,0:25:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看看我们收到多少投诉{\r}\NLook, we've got so many complaint
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.46,0:25:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}未经批准，就擅自行动{\r}\NYou took action without my approval
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.62,0:25:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}滥用暴力，伤害疑犯，叫我怎么保住你？{\r}\Nused violence to hurt suspects. How can I protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.54,0:26:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}何雪玲督察，你这一次令我太失望了{\r}\NInspector Ho Hsueh-ling, you've let me down
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.46,0:26:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起，长官{\r}\NSorry, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.46,0:26:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在说对不起...有什么用？{\r}\NWhat good to say sorry now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.38,0:26:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你当了警察这么久{\r}\NHow long have you been in the police force?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.70,0:26:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以你跟阿修的关系{\r}\NWith your relationship with Hsiu
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.02,0:26:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}根本就不应该办这件案{\r}\Nyou shouldn't handle this case
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.90,0:26:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我跟阿修还没有正式结婚{\r}\NWe're legally...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.46,0:26:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}法律上不算是夫妻{\r}\Nstill unmarried
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.58,0:26:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}住口{\r}\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.54,0:26:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}讲法律？我们当警察随时随地都可能殉职{\r}\NTo talk about law, we'll all die martrs
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.06,0:26:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}如果每一个人都要报仇{\r}\NVengeance makes us
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.66,0:26:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟流氓有什么分别？{\r}\Nno different from rascal
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.46,0:26:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你没有资格当警察{\r}\NYou're unfit to be a policeman
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.46,0:26:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对不起，长官{\r}\NSorry, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.90,0:26:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}何雪玲督察这一次行动是经过我口头批准{\r}\NInsp Ho's operation got my verbal approval
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.26,0:26:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}整件事情我最清楚{\r}\NI know the whole thing well
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.90,0:26:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不用维护她{\r}\NDon't cover her up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.46,0:26:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我只是觉得我需要负责{\r}\NI only feel that I've a responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.82,0:26:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，你这么喜欢负责，你搞定它{\r}\NGood fix it then
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.22,0:26:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}再有什么差错，小心你自己的前途{\r}\NIf anything goes wrong again, mind your future
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.98,0:26:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.50,0:27:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我替你背这个黑锅也没所谓{\r}\NI don't mind bearing the blame for you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.54,0:27:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可是有时候办案不是靠冲动就行{\r}\NBut remember foolhardiness doesn't always work
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.10,0:27:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官 德叔，怎么样？{\r}\NMr. Huang! Uncle Te, how's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.46,0:27:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有线索{\r}\NWe've a gIue
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.34,0:27:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}潮洲雄会在两点钟{\r}\NSwatow Hsiung will leave HK
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.46,0:27:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}会在三门仔码头坐船离开香港{\r}\Nat Sam Mun Pier at two
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.78,0:27:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老兄，还有多久才开船？{\r}\NBuddy, when will the ship sail?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.54,0:27:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}搬完这几桶就行了{\r}\NAfter these drums have been moved
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.06,0:27:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}潮洲雄{\r}\NSwatow Hsiung
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.38,0:27:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不许动，快开船{\r}\NDon't move! Sail quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.14,0:27:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开船，否则一枪打死你{\r}\NSail, or I'll shoot you dead
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.86,0:27:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}解缆{\r}\NRelease the rope
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.46,0:27:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老大，你不要开枪，全船都是汽油{\r}\NBrother, don't shoot, it's loaded with gasoline
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.46,0:27:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一家大小全在船上{\r}\NMy whole family's on it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.82,0:27:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}求求你，你千万不要开枪{\r}\NDon't shoot. I beg you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.58,0:27:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}解缆，快一点{\r}\NRelease the rope, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.98,0:28:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}去死吧{\r}\NGo to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.74,0:28:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要动{\r}\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.02,0:28:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这么做会犯法{\r}\NYou're violating the law
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.70,0:28:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泰利叫船家开船驶回岸去{\r}\NTerry, tell the bastard to bring the boat back to shore
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.14,0:28:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，把现场的证物全收拾好带回去{\r}\NYu, keep the evidence on the spot and bring it back
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.42,0:28:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}知道了黄长官{\r}\NYes, Mr.Huang
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.78,0:28:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}船主，把牌照和身份证拿出来{\r}\NCaptain, show me your license and I.D
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.54,0:28:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}长官，不关我的事{\r}\NNot my fault, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.70,0:29:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没事了，先驶回岸去{\r}\NBack to the shore
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.38,0:29:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上了岸再替你落口供{\r}\NWe'll take your statement then
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.06,0:29:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也很想杀他{\r}\NI wanted to kill him too
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.18,0:29:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别再说了{\r}\NNo more
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.62,0:29:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是我们是警察{\r}\NWe're police
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.82,0:29:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}干什么？{\r}\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.58,0:29:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老鬼德，花旗参那一件事我知道的{\r}\NOId Te. I know the American ginseng case
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.50,0:29:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放我一条生路，大家都好{\r}\NGive me a chance. It's for everyone's good
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.50,0:29:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你的废话真多，拜山时再说{\r}\NSave your nonsense for the Tomb Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.46,0:29:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官...{\r}\NMr.Huang...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.34,0:29:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把这些全部搞定{\r}\NFix all these
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.90,0:29:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官，你知不知道花旗参的事？{\r}\NMr.Huang, do you know the American ginseng case?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.62,0:29:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官{\r}\NMr.Huang
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.46,0:29:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}聪明的你就放我一马，否则大家同归于尽{\r}\NBe smart and let me go or we'll both penrish
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.98,0:29:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开枪打死我好了{\r}\NKill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.46,0:29:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看你怎么写报告，开枪吧{\r}\NSee how you'll make your report
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.38,0:30:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你走{\r}\NGet away...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.14,0:30:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}抢枪... 不要动{\r}\NA snatcher... Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.30,0:30:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}过去看看他{\r}\NGo and see him
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.46,0:30:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}过来这边，你留在这里看着他{\r}\NOver here, you stay to watch him
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.46,0:30:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\NYes, Madam
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.58,0:30:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你过来，过来这边划位{\r}\NCome here! Come here to mark the seat
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.90,0:30:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要让其他人走过来{\r}\NStop the others from coming
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.02,0:30:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老鬼德，你是不是给吓坏了{\r}\NOId Te, were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.46,0:30:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这柄枪要拿回来做证物{\r}\NYou need this gun for evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.46,0:30:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是...忘记了{\r}\NOh. I forgot
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.14,0:30:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}吓呆了{\r}\NHe was stunned
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.30,0:30:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这些咖啡是一个巴西朋友送给我，试一下{\r}\NThis coffee came from my friend in Brazil. Try it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.70,0:30:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢长官{\r}\NThank you, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.34,0:30:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我看过昨天那一件事的报告{\r}\NI've read the report on yesterday's incidence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.82,0:30:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}韦长官{\r}\NMr.Wei
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.82,0:30:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一件案虽然拿不到满分{\r}\NWe got no fulI marks
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.34,0:30:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是我已经很满意{\r}\Nbut I'm satisfied with the result
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.42,0:30:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}可惜留不到活口，不然可以问多一点线索{\r}\NHad we captured on alive, we could get more cIues
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.42,0:30:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我就是喜欢你这点，对自己要求这么严格{\r}\NI like you for your serious attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.70,0:30:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你已经够忙了，放两天假休息一下{\r}\NYou're already so busy. Take 2 days' leave
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.46,0:30:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢长官{\r}\NThank you, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.98,0:31:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有鱼上钓了，我钓到它了{\r}\NA fish has swallowed the bait
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.10,0:31:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你过来看看{\r}\NGo and see
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.38,0:31:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好大条{\r}\NA big fish
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.42,0:31:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你也会钓到鱼，鱼之中这一条算笨了{\r}\NEven you've caught it, must be a stupid fish
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.26,0:31:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不知道是你笨还是它笨？{\r}\NSo you're stupider!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.46,0:31:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那样也可以 它快要掉下去{\r}\NIs that possible? It's going to drop down
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.02,0:31:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点捉着它 小心点...{\r}\NCatch it at once. Be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.70,0:31:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}看错了，原来鱼也是这么古惑{\r}\NI've seen it. So it's a crafty fish
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.38,0:31:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是{\r}\NIs it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.46,0:31:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}海里都是笨鱼，再钓别一条好了{\r}\NThere's no lack of stupid fish. Let's catch
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.46,0:31:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我跟你出来玩也希望你能开心点{\r}\NI daren't convey anything to you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.06,0:31:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}干么还那么闷{\r}\Nbut you can trust me
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.58,0:31:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我教你驾帆船，以后跟你一起横渡太平洋{\r}\NLet's me teach you yatching. Some day we'll cross the Pacific
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.62,0:31:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来...{\r}\NCome!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.54,0:32:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不行...{\r}\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.62,0:32:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}转...{\r}\NTurn...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.74,0:32:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}转哪一个方向？{\r}\NWhich way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.86,0:32:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}转这一边吗？{\r}\NThis away?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.78,0:32:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对了，转...{\r}\NRight. Turn
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.50,0:32:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是不是这样转...？{\r}\NThis way?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.46,0:32:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}继续...{\r}\NGo on
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.90,0:32:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我行了{\r}\NI did it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.46,0:32:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}德叔{\r}\NUncle Te
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.46,0:32:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，有空要多点陪伴爱美{\r}\NYu, spend more time on Amy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.54,0:32:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不然很容易分手{\r}\Nto strengthen the ties
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.14,0:32:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也想{\r}\NI wish I could
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.38,0:32:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁叫我当警察？{\r}\NBut I'm a policeman
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.46,0:32:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我先走了{\r}\NExcuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.66,0:32:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，拜拜{\r}\NOkay! Bye-bye
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.02,0:33:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是阿有{\r}\NThis is Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.22,0:33:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事？{\r}\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.02,0:33:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官{\r}\NMr.Huang
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.98,0:33:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我亲眼看到德叔跟几个洋鬼子买卖毒物{\r}\NI've caught Uncle Te dealing drug with foreigner
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.10,0:33:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有可能{\r}\NImpossible
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.14,0:33:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是真的，我拍了录影带做证{\r}\NIt's true. I've the video tape for evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.58,0:33:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不如马上采取行动？你认为怎么样{\r}\NLet's make immediate action. What do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.14,0:33:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要，这一件事可能牵涉很大{\r}\NNo, it could be complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.90,0:33:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你明天把录影带回警察局给我看看{\r}\NBring all the tapes to the station for me to see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.82,0:33:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有急事？{\r}\NAnything important?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.14,0:34:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小事情，我先送你回去{\r}\NNothing serious. I'll take you home
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.06,0:34:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走吧{\r}\NLet's go
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.46,0:34:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}仙蒂姐叫我提醒你，今天是爱美的生日{\r}\NCindy wants me to remind you today is Amy birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.70,0:34:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道了，我当然知道了{\r}\NI know. I know
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.46,0:34:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}蛋糕和花都帮你买好，去逗她求她原谅你{\r}\NSee the cake and flowers is ready. Go and be pardon
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.70,0:34:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还想什么？快上车{\r}\NWhat are you waiting for! Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.94,0:34:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}女人，你不求不拜很容易拜拜...{\r}\NGirls have to be soothed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.94,0:34:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}知道了，三八{\r}\NI know, you nosey
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.30,0:34:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}快点去，爱美快要下班了，走吧{\r}\NGo now. Amy will be off duty soon
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.94,0:34:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真多事{\r}\NYou're meddlesome
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.62,0:34:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泡妞只准十五分钟{\r}\NOnly 15 minutes for fooling around
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.62,0:34:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}头等机票两张 谢谢{\r}\NTwo first class airtickets. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.46,0:34:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谢谢你{\r}\NThank you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.66,0:34:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爱美{\r}\NAmy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.86,0:35:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}先生，买机票吗？{\r}\NCan I help you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.50,0:35:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，我想买两张机票跟我的女朋友去旅行{\r}\NYes. I want 2 tickets for a trip with my girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.78,0:35:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}因为是她的生日，祝你生日快乐{\r}\NIt's her birthday. Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.38,0:35:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}送给你的{\r}\NIt's yours
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.90,0:35:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拍了些什么？让我先看看{\r}\NWhat's it on the tape? Let me show it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.74,0:35:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}回去煮些什么给我吃？{\r}\NWhat are you going to cook for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}吃完饭再吃蛋糕{\r}\NLet's eat cakes after dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.18,0:35:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你干么看我的录影带？开门{\r}\NDon't touch my videotape recorder! Open the door
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.74,0:35:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}开门 干什么？{\r}\NOpen up! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.94,0:35:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不关你的事{\r}\NIt's none of your business
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.46,0:35:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}出来...{\r}\NCome out...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.86,0:36:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁叫你看我的录影带？{\r}\NWho told you to watch my videotape
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.46,0:36:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，连这么严重的事也不告诉我？{\r}\NWell, you're keeping such a serious thing from me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.02,0:36:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事？{\r}\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.74,0:36:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有没有把我当做兄弟？{\r}\NAre you taking me for your brother
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.86,0:36:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你说...{\r}\NSpeak up...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.46,0:36:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你真笨，德叔是你师父{\r}\NUncle Te's your master
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.46,0:36:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他有没有告诉你他贩买海洛英{\r}\Nbut he's keeping it from you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.62,0:36:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}哪就是不相信我，是不是？{\r}\NIt means he doesn't trust me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.46,0:36:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}很难说，你把德叔看成是你老爸{\r}\NWho knows? You're taking him for you dad
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.66,0:36:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我怎么知道你有没有份{\r}\NHow do I know you're an accessory?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.46,0:36:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一种勾当，会说我有份{\r}\NWould I be an accessory to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.94,0:36:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我跟你一起出生入死这么久{\r}\NI went through everything with you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.70,0:36:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这样也怀疑我？{\r}\Nand you suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.46,0:36:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你...你这么冲动，我怎么可以告诉你？{\r}\NYou're so impulsive. How could I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.38,0:36:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}告诉你岂不是害了你？{\r}\NIt would only ruin you
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.14,0:36:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你现在怕什么，怕什么？{\r}\NWhat have you to fear now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.66,0:36:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也不怕，你怕什么？管他是老虎{\r}\NI'm not afraid either. Be he a tiger
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.70,0:36:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就算是我的亲生爸爸{\r}\Nor my own dad
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.38,0:36:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他贩买海洛英我一样要捉他，你知不知？{\r}\NI'll take him if he sells drug
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.38,0:36:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我马上就去捉他{\r}\NI'll go and arrest him right now
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.18,0:36:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放手{\r}\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.06,0:36:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你别这么冲动好不好{\r}\NDon't be so impulsive!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.70,0:36:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你再这么冲动就什么都被你破坏了{\r}\NAny rash action will ruin everything
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.58,0:36:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们是不是兄弟？{\r}\NAren't we brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.30,0:37:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在告诉你，这事只有我跟黄长官知道{\r}\NListen this is only between me and Mr.Huang
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.06,0:37:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有我{\r}\NAnd me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.06,0:37:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}对了...{\r}\NYes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.78,0:37:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}记着，有什么发现，不要私自行动，OK？{\r}\NRemember, don't take individual action if you discover anything. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.46,0:37:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}糟了，我要找爱美解释{\r}\NBad. I must explain to Amy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.22,0:37:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别乱来{\r}\NDon't do anything foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.34,0:37:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你听我说{\r}\NListen
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.78,0:37:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好痛{\r}\NIt hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.86,0:37:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你再不走我就报警，说有个警察擅闯民居{\r}\NGo now, or I'll call the police and accuse you of trespassing
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.62,0:37:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不是这样开玩笑吧？{\r}\NYou must be joking
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.82,0:37:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}谁跟你开玩笑，跟你的朋友玩好了{\r}\NWho's joking with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.14,0:37:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爱美{\r}\NAmy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.90,0:37:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不想看到你，走{\r}\NI won't see you anymore. Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.02,0:37:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的手{\r}\NMy hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.14,0:37:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你赖死不走是吗？我走{\r}\NYou're not going? I will
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.46,0:37:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}干什么？{\r}\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.46,0:37:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不许动{\r}\NDon't go
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.46,0:37:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你当我是犯人？{\r}\NAre you taking me for a criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.46,0:37:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，我控告你蓄意伤害警务人员自尊心{\r}\NYes. I sue you for willful damage to a policeman's pride
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.02,0:38:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在盘问你{\r}\NI must question you now
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.46,0:38:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我追了你十多条街，说了几十句对不起{\r}\NI've followed you all the way and kept saying 'sorry'
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.66,0:38:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还想我怎么样？{\r}\NWhat else do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.78,0:38:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}方长官，我想你尊重一下我{\r}\NMr.Fan, I want you to have some respect for me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.62,0:38:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你心情好的时候就来找我{\r}\NYou come to see me when you're in the mood
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.86,0:38:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你心情不好的时候就扔下我{\r}\NYou leave me behind and say sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.98,0:38:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说声对不起就算数{\r}\Nwhen you're not
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.46,0:38:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你把我看成是什么人？{\r}\NWhat are you taking me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.46,0:38:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}当你是我的女朋友，值得我对你说对不起{\r}\NMy girlfriend, worthy of my respect
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.30,0:38:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}值得我用行动来表示对我有多重要{\r}\NHave my action to show how important you're to me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.46,0:38:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在开始陪你到明天早上{\r}\NI'll keep you company till tomorrow morning
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.70,0:38:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}警察也不做，够了没有？{\r}\NI'll quit as a policeman. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.46,0:38:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不够{\r}\NNo
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.58,0:38:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}市民也不做，街也不去，连传呼机也不要{\r}\NI'll give you as a citizen to go out
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.98,0:38:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟所有人绝交，我绝不放你{\r}\NI'll break with anyone else, but I won't let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.62,0:38:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你快点放了我{\r}\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.22,0:38:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不放，今天晚上一于重色轻友{\r}\NNo, you mean everything to me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.86,0:38:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不放手我怎么煮饭？死相{\r}\NI can't cook if you don't let me go, jerk
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.38,0:38:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，你说得对，让我放了你{\r}\NRight, right, I must let you go
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.46,0:38:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}等我先看看你有没有受伤{\r}\NLet me see if you're hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.50,0:38:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}警察非礼，罪加一等{\r}\NA policeman gets more sentence for indecent assault
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.74,0:38:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}撤职也值得{\r}\NI couldn't care less
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.46,0:39:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}信有，你搞什么鬼？进来帮帮我{\r}\NYu, what are you up to? Come and help
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.26,0:39:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在给你弄一份生日礼物{\r}\NI'm preparing a birthday gift for you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.94,0:39:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来吃东西{\r}\NCome and eat
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.18,0:39:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}大礼物来了{\r}\NThe big gift is here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.10,0:39:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我可不可爱{\r}\NAm I sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.46,0:39:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}整个人送给你{\r}\NTake me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.58,0:39:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真核突...{\r}\NDisgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.42,0:39:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉，有没有锁匙？{\r}\NShirley, have you got the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.06,0:39:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以前就没有{\r}\NYes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.30,0:39:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一个柜阿修一直都不让我打开{\r}\Nbut Hsiu never allowed me to open it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.50,0:39:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也不知道有什么放在里面{\r}\Nand I don't know what it contains
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.86,0:40:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你送给他的？{\r}\NDid you give him this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.38,0:40:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他什么事都放在心里，从来不跟我说{\r}\NHe always kept everything to himself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.42,0:40:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一千多万{\r}\NOver $10 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.58,0:40:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}以他的家当和收入，没有可能有这么多钱{\r}\NImpossible for a man of his family background!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.34,0:40:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有两个护照，要来什么用？{\r}\NAnd these 2 passports! What are they for?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.70,0:40:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这些钱是用不正当手段赚回来的{\r}\NThis must be ill-gotten money
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.10,0:40:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这两个护照是预备在被人揭发的时候...{\r}\NThese passports are to help use another identity
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.18,0:40:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}随时可以用另一个身份离开香港{\r}\Nto get out of HK, in case of need
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.70,0:40:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希望我的想法是错的{\r}\NWish my reasoning was wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.42,0:41:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}最近我接到线报{\r}\NI've recently got a tip-off that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.10,0:41:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说我们的部门有人利用职权贩卖海洛英{\r}\Nsomeone abused his power for dope-push
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.46,0:41:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一直以为他很忠直，原来什么都是假的{\r}\NI thought he was honest
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.50,0:41:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉，我很明白你的心情{\r}\NShirley, I know how you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.90,0:41:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}希望你可以面对现实{\r}\NPlease face up to reality
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.46,0:41:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿修的确有可疑，不过你放心{\r}\NThere's indeed something wrong with him
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.14,0:41:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我一定帮你，一定帮你查出真相{\r}\Nbut I'll help you find out the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.30,0:42:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}先生，买支旗...{\r}\NBuy a flag, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.06,0:42:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟着前面的白色车{\r}\NFollow that white car in front
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.46,0:42:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}皇家警察，你不想着警察局的事吗？{\r}\NRoyal HK policeman, no more police affair
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.10,0:42:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我才不理它的死活{\r}\NNo
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.46,0:42:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}今天晚上我整个人都属于你{\r}\NI'm all yours tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.74,0:42:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}滚开{\r}\NGET LOST
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.50,0:43:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}警察{\r}\NPolice
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.18,0:43:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把枪放下{\r}\NDrop your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.14,0:43:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老鬼德，把你的枪也扔掉{\r}\NDrop your gun too, old Te
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.46,0:43:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泰利，我...{\r}\NTerry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.46,0:43:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}留下来跟法官说，把枪扔到海里去{\r}\NStay to speak to the judge. Filing it to see
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.10,0:43:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拿你的手铐把两个洋鬼子铐上{\r}\NGet you handcuffs and put them on
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.02,0:43:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把他们铐上{\r}\Nthose two foreigners
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.18,0:44:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泰利{\r}\NTerry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.30,0:44:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你贩毒？{\r}\NYou're trafficking in drugs
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.42,0:44:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你身为警务人员，竟然知法犯法{\r}\NAs a policeman, you know the law and violate it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.14,0:44:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我年轻的时候也跟你一样这么大火气{\r}\NI was as hot-tempered when I was young
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.46,0:44:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我明白{\r}\NI understood
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.22,0:44:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不明白你为什么要这样做？{\r}\NWhy did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.34,0:44:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我从学堂出来就一直跟着你{\r}\NI've followed you since I left school
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.46,0:44:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我当你是我师父，当你是我的爸爸{\r}\NI took you for my master, my dad
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.18,0:44:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是今天我跟你的关系到此为止{\r}\Nbut now it's all over between us
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.94,0:44:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我要拉你{\r}\NYou're under arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.42,0:44:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}拉我？当年我比你还勇{\r}\NArrest me? I was braver than you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.86,0:44:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为了拉几个小卒，你看我得到些什么？{\r}\NWhat did I get for arresting some small frys
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.46,0:44:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}两个破奖章{\r}\N2 lousy medals
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.90,0:45:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}翻风落雨就痛得我一整个晚上都睡不着{\r}\NWhen the weather's bad, it hurts and I can't sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.10,0:45:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他们坐完牢出来，不也是一样贩毒{\r}\NThey did it again once they got discharged
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.22,0:45:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也是个小卒{\r}\NI am a small fry too
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.90,0:45:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不理是小卒还是大魔头{\r}\NA small fry or a big shot
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.62,0:45:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}总之栽在我手里一样没情讲{\r}\NI don't care
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.46,0:45:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泰利，你还年轻，你有理想是对的{\r}\NTerry, you're still young and you're your idea
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.46,0:45:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}但是当你好像我家里的环境，这么需要钱{\r}\NWhen you reach my age and are
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.50,0:45:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我什么也不懂，什么也没有{\r}\Nin my straitened circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.90,0:45:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你就会知道钱是那么重要{\r}\NYou'll see how important money is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.02,0:45:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你住口，你不用找借口原谅自己{\r}\NShut up! Don't find an excuse for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.46,0:45:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泰利，放阿叔一马{\r}\NTerry, let me go
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.46,0:45:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不可以放你，德叔{\r}\NSorry, Uncle Te
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.90,0:45:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道你对我好，我也不想{\r}\NI know you're nice to me, but I've no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.34,0:45:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官，我在赤柱圣士提反湾{\r}\NI caught Te dealing in drugs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.46,0:46:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}捉到德叔跟两个洋鬼子交易{\r}\Nwith 2 foreigners in Stephen Bay, Stanley
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.70,0:46:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}来...{\r}\NCome on
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.62,0:48:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}停手...{\r}\NStop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.18,0:48:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}小子，你们动就会死{\r}\NDon't move, or you'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.90,0:48:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官{\r}\NSir
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.86,0:48:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}就是这两个洋鬼子跟德叔交易毒品{\r}\Nthese 2 foreigners dealt in drugs with Uncle Te
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.98,0:48:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经拍了录影带做证据{\r}\NI've got the tape for evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.22,0:48:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，你做得很好，立了大功{\r}\NWell done! You're done a great credit
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.90,0:48:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}把德叔铐起来{\r}\NHandcuff Uncle Te
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.50,0:48:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.58,0:49:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们走吧，我跟你的波士解决一切{\r}\NI'll fix everything with your boss. Leave now
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.18,0:49:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好的{\r}\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.58,0:49:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你干么要杀死他？{\r}\NWhy do you want to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.82,0:49:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他不死你就死定了{\r}\NYou'll die for sure if he doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.98,0:49:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我宁愿坐牢...{\r}\NI'd rather go to jail...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.30,0:50:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}也不愿杀死他{\r}\Nthan to kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.06,0:50:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是我至好的手下，我一定会罩着你的{\r}\NYou're my best aide. I'll cover you up
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.22,0:50:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不干了{\r}\NI quit
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.50,0:50:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}替我办完了这件案再说{\r}\NFinish this case for me first
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.38,0:50:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这里的事你知道怎么处理，就这么决定{\r}\NYou know how to handle the things here
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.18,0:50:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你曾经向我亲口保证过{\r}\NYou gave personal assurance that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.46,0:50:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}说这一次的合作一定不会出事{\r}\Neverything would be okay
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.46,0:50:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我保证的是那些货，没有说过当你的保母{\r}\NOnly about the stuff. I'm not your nanny
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.58,0:50:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真是高估了你的实力{\r}\NI've overassessed you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.90,0:50:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}连一个小子也搞不定{\r}\NYou can't even finish a kid
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.82,0:50:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我跟你的合作到此为至{\r}\NNow the co-operation is over between us
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.18,0:50:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们纽约的市场那么大{\r}\NOur market in New York is so big
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.30,0:51:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}香港这边有很多人争着做我的拍档{\r}\NMany in HK would vie to be my sidekick
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.42,0:51:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}OK，没问题{\r}\NOkay, no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.18,0:51:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不过我告诉你{\r}\NListen
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.82,0:51:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}凡是我碰过的生意没有人敢再碰{\r}\Nno one dare touch any deals I touched
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.18,0:51:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}香港是我的，美国市场不单止你们{\r}\NHong Kong is mine, and you're not the only market in USA
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.98,0:51:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}马上离开香港回纽约去{\r}\NGet out of HK and return to New York
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.30,0:51:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}慢着，米高{\r}\NHold it, Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.06,0:51:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我来这里是赚钱，不是找仇人{\r}\NI came here to make money, not to make enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.02,0:51:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，我再相信你一次{\r}\NOkay, I'll trust you one more time
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.34,0:51:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，如果要合作就帮我做一点事{\r}\NWell, if you want co-operation, do one thing for me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.46,0:51:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明天晚上我要二百斤货{\r}\NI want 200 kilos of stuff tomorrow night
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.10,0:51:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一个是我的户口号码{\r}\NThis is my A/C No.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.38,0:51:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明天早上你存了钱，晚上可以收到货{\r}\NCredit the money into it. You'll g et the stuff tomorrow night
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.06,0:51:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这个凶手一定跑不掉{\r}\NThe killer can never get away
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.94,0:51:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}手足们一定可以捉到他{\r}\NWe can get hold of him for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.46,0:51:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}早安{\r}\NMorning!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.46,0:52:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}干么你们每一个人都苦口苦脸{\r}\NWhat's wrong? Why are you all wearing a stone face?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.18,0:52:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}死了老爸是不是？{\r}\NA bereavement?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.14,0:52:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有 阿有，进来{\r}\NAh Yu. Ah Yu, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.18,0:52:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉，请你先出去一会{\r}\NShirley, please go out for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.86,0:52:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，关门，谢谢{\r}\NAh Yu, close the door please
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.46,0:52:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我查到阿修贩毒{\r}\NI've ascertained Hsiu's drug-trafficking
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.10,0:52:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真的？莎莉知不知道？{\r}\NIs that so? Does Shirley know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.34,0:52:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不敢肯定{\r}\NI'm not too sure
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.70,0:52:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}会不会她也有份？{\r}\NWould she be an accessory?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.46,0:52:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想我们以后都要小心点{\r}\NWe must take more care from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.50,0:52:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我真不敢相信莎莉都有份{\r}\NI don't think Shirley has a hand on it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.46,0:52:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一盒是德叔跟毒贩交易的录影带{\r}\NHere's a cassette of Te's drug-trafficking
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.50,0:53:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我想这一件事，事关重大{\r}\NIt's of serious consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.54,0:53:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}之前有阿修，现在是德叔{\r}\NFormerly it was Hsiu, now it's Uncle Te
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.46,0:53:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}究竟还有多少人牵涉在里面，我也不知道{\r}\NHow many more are involved I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.38,0:53:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，你还有没有其他证据{\r}\NYu, have you got any other evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.46,0:53:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我过了一盒带子放在爱美家里{\r}\NI've put a tape at Amy's
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.46,0:53:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是吗？{\r}\NIs that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.26,0:53:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不用怕{\r}\NDon't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.14,0:53:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}爱美也不知道我放了一盒带了在她家里{\r}\NAmy knows nothing about it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.46,0:53:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我们要尽快把那盒带子拿回来{\r}\NWe must get it back as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.70,0:53:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}为了爱美的安全，你不要再对任何人说{\r}\NFor Amy's safety, don't tell anyone about it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.26,0:53:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我知道该怎么做了{\r}\NI know what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.22,0:53:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉，请你进来{\r}\NShirley, please come in
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.42,0:53:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，有一件事要跟你说{\r}\NYu, I want to talk to you
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.46,0:53:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不要冲动，你要冷静一点{\r}\NKeep cool
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.30,0:53:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}昨天晚上发生了一件事{\r}\NSomething happened last night
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.46,0:53:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么事？{\r}\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.70,0:53:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}进来{\r}\NCome in
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.42,0:53:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官{\r}\NMr.Huang
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.06,0:53:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉，这是重要证物，替我放在保险箱里{\r}\NShirley, put this important item in a safe
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.34,0:54:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不怕她是德叔的同党{\r}\NAren't you afraid she might be Te's accompany
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.62,0:54:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不会吧{\r}\NImpossible
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.98,0:54:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}昨天泰利被人杀死了{\r}\NTerry was killed yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.38,0:54:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}什么？{\r}\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.74,0:54:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他知道老鬼德的事，这就...{\r}\NHe knew about OId Te
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.46,0:54:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我出去一会{\r}\NI must go out for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.46,0:54:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要走，老鬼德，你这个死家伙{\r}\NOId Te, hold it! You creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.46,0:54:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你害死了泰利，我打死你{\r}\NYou ruined Terry. I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.78,0:54:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有{\r}\NAh Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.70,0:54:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你疯，德叔当泰利是自己的孩子，你误会{\r}\NAre you crazy? Uncle Te's taking Terry for his own son. You're mistaken
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.26,0:54:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，你别胡思乱想，他怎么会这样做？{\r}\NYu, don't get the wrong idea. He won't do that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.42,0:54:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你疯了？{\r}\NAre you crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.46,0:54:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}停手{\r}\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.46,0:54:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}发生什么事？{\r}\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.62,0:54:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他当警察也贩毒，有什么事干不出？{\r}\NA policeman trafficking in drugs can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.46,0:54:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别吵，大家自己兄弟，有话好说{\r}\NQuiet! We're all friends. Let's talk it over
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.94,0:54:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放开我{\r}\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.86,0:54:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有证据证明你贩毒{\r}\NI've proof of your drug-trafficking
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.42,0:55:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我已经报告黄长官，我一定指证你{\r}\NI've already reported to Mr.Huang. I'll testify against you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.06,0:55:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，不要这么冲动{\r}\NYu, don't be impulsive
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.98,0:55:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你是曾向我报告，但我没有看到证据之前{\r}\NYou did report to me, but I can't accuse Te
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.86,0:55:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不可以一口说定是德叔{\r}\Nbefore I see the evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.46,0:55:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不用看了，一定是他{\r}\NIt must be him
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.66,0:55:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我有你跟贩毒交易的录影带{\r}\NI've got tapes of your drug-trafficking
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.50,0:55:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你胡说{\r}\NNonsense
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.74,0:55:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉，放给他看{\r}\NShirley, run it for him
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.78,0:55:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放给他看{\r}\NRun it for him
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.22,0:55:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你还是这样...{\r}\NDon't ...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.46,0:55:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}放吧{\r}\NRun it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.54,0:55:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么没有？{\r}\NHow come?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.46,0:55:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}原来是有的，我的录影带被人换了{\r}\NObviously the cassette has been swapped
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.26,0:55:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}换什么，证据呢？{\r}\NWhat? Where's the evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.46,0:55:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}作贼心虚，我说你才有嫌疑{\r}\NYou yourself are under suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.66,0:55:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你自己作贼心虚{\r}\NYou're exposing your own crime
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.06,0:56:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}上一次修哥之死{\r}\NLast time Hsiu got killed
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.18,0:56:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}是因为你在他的车上装了烟幕弹{\r}\Nbecause you planted a smoke bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.30,0:56:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一次泰利的死是因为你擅离职守{\r}\NThis time Terry got killed because you abandoned your duty
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.46,0:56:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你有什么解释？{\r}\NWhat explanation can you give?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.46,0:56:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}守他的贮物柜{\r}\NSearch his locker!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.18,0:56:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我亲眼看见他把海洛英放在里面，开...{\r}\NI saw him putting heroin in...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.06,0:56:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我也看见你把海洛英放在贮物柜里面{\r}\NI also saw you put heroin into the locker
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.94,0:56:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}要搜就大家一起搜{\r}\NLet's search together
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.62,0:56:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我怕你吗？你死定了，把锁匙拿来{\r}\NI'm not afraid. You're finished. Give me the key
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.34,0:56:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别乱来{\r}\NDon't try anything foolish
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.58,0:56:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}走开{\r}\NKeep away!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.46,0:56:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}德叔，把锁匙拿出来{\r}\NUncle Te, the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.06,0:56:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}山鸡{\r}\NPheasant
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.98,0:56:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不好意思，德叔{\r}\NSorry, Uncle Te
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.46,0:56:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}冷静{\r}\NKeep cool
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.62,0:56:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不要乱来{\r}\NDon't mess around
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.66,0:56:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}德叔，真的是你{\r}\NUncle Te, you really did it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.22,0:56:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你收起了我的书还说不见了{\r}\NYou put aside my book and said it was missing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.46,0:56:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你搜清楚一点行不行？{\r}\NWill you search more thoroughly?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.86,0:56:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}全部搜过了，什么都没有{\r}\NWe've searched everything. There's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.02,0:56:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}搜他的家，一定有的{\r}\NLet's search his home
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.46,0:56:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，那你的贮物柜...{\r}\NAh Yu, your locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.38,0:56:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}打开来看看{\r}\NOpen it and see
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.26,0:56:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好了{\r}\NOkay
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.14,0:57:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}搜吧{\r}\NSearch!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.46,0:57:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}真是你的 不是我的{\r}\NYou really did it. No
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.70,0:57:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}冷静一点...{\r}\NYu, calm down
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.98,0:57:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不是想告诉我这一包是面粉吧？{\r}\NAre you going to tell me this is flour?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.22,0:57:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这东西不是我的，你嫁祸给我{\r}\NThis bag is not mine
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.46,0:57:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}冷静一点{\r}\NCalm down
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.58,0:57:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你相信我，莎莉，相信我{\r}\NBelieve me, Shirley, believe me
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.50,0:57:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在我什么人也不会再相信{\r}\NNow I won't trust anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.10,0:57:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}只会相信事实，相信证据{\r}\NI only believe in truth and evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.10,0:57:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我现在用藏毒的罪名拘捕你{\r}\NYou're arrested for drug possession
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.74,0:57:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}莎莉，我知道陷害我的不只德叔一个{\r}\NShirley, I know Te is not alone in the frame-up
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.82,0:57:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那一班人我早晚会找出来，你小心一点{\r}\NSoon I'll seek them out! Watch out
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.62,0:57:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你这不是说我们吗？你冤枉好人{\r}\NDo you mean us? Don't frame us
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.74,0:57:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你自己不好就算了，别把大家都拖...{\r}\NDon't get us involved because you're evil
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.46,0:57:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}别吵，这里是街市？{\r}\NQuiet, this is not a market
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.62,0:57:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们是纪律部队{\r}\NYou're the Discipline Unit
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.98,0:57:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有跟德叔互相指控，我会撤查{\r}\NI'll investigate the accusation between Yu and Uncle Te
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.78,0:58:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你们也是一样，要接受内部调查{\r}\NYou'll also be subject to internal investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.78,0:58:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是毒品调查科特别行动组督察何雪玲{\r}\NI'm drug Investigation Special Operation Insp Ho
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.62,0:58:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我怀疑你藏毒，叫什么名字{\r}\NYou're suspected of drug possession. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.26,0:58:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}方信有{\r}\NFan Shun-yu
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.94,0:58:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}职业{\r}\NOccupation
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.54,0:58:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}香港皇家警察队雇员{\r}\NA member of the Royal Hong Kong Police Force
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.18,0:58:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}隶属毒品调查科特别行动组{\r}\Nwith the Drug Investigation Dept of the Special Operations
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.38,0:58:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}住在哪里？{\r}\NWhere do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.66,0:58:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}明知故问{\r}\NYou know it already
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.14,0:58:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你曾经是警察，你应该知道...{\r}\NAs a policeman, you should know...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.54,0:58:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}这一点我比你更清楚{\r}\NI know better in this respect
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.02,0:58:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我在你的贮物柜找到海洛英，你怎么解释{\r}\NI've discovered heroin in your locker, how do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.02,0:58:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}怎么解释？我是被人插赃嫁祸的{\r}\NI was framed. Why should I explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.38,0:58:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我没有藏毒，我不用接受你的盘问{\r}\NPossess no drugs, why should I be question
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.30,0:58:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有一样证据支持我可以相信你的话{\r}\NThere's no evidence to support your state
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.46,0:58:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那就是你有证据可以指证我了{\r}\NYou mean you've proof against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.30,0:58:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想清楚有什么可以证明你是无辜的{\r}\NCan you think of anything to prove your innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.58,0:58:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}法律是要讲证据的{\r}\NLaw requires evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.34,0:58:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你所说的一切都会作为是呈堂证供{\r}\NAll your statement may be used as evidence in court
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.34,0:58:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}好，我说{\r}\NOkay, I'll give my statement
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.94,0:58:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我藏毒、贩毒、走私{\r}\NI deal in drugs, smuggling and
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.70,0:58:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}杀人放火、打劫{\r}\Nresort to killing, arson and robbery
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.82,0:58:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你写好了，例行手续，你写吧{\r}\NTake it down as a matter of routine! Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.42,0:58:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}呈堂证供是吗？写吧{\r}\NEvidence in Court? Take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.42,0:58:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有{\r}\NAh Yu
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.58,0:59:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我的名字叫方信有，我不认识你{\r}\NMy name is Fan Shun-yu, I don't know you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.18,0:59:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我怀疑督察何雪玲串谋害我，写吧{\r}\NI suspect Insp Ho Hsueh-ling's conspiracy against me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.22,0:59:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}写...告我好了{\r}\NTake it down! Sue me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.38,0:59:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在是八八年十月二十日下午三点{\r}\NThe time is 20th Oct 1988 at 3 p.m
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.38,0:59:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我是扫毒组探员方信有，探员编号3368{\r}\NI'm Anti-Narcotics Bureau detective Fan Shun-yu No. 3368
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.06,0:59:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我怀疑同组警长冯建德贩毒{\r}\NI suspect my Sergeant Feng Chien-te of drug-trafficking
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.46,0:59:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}经过三天的调查和跟踪{\r}\NAs a result of 3 days probe and trace
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.82,0:59:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在发现他在渡海轮上{\r}\NI've discovered him dealing in drugs with...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.46,0:59:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}跟两个身份未明的外籍人士进行毒品交易{\r}\N2 unidentified foreigners on a ferry
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.06,1:00:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}据我暂时的推测{\r}\Ndeduced that he used his detective identity
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.30,1:00:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}他利用扫毒组探员身份掩饰进行毒品交易{\r}\Nto cover up his trafficking activities
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.22,1:01:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官？{\r}\NMr.Huang
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.18,1:01:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官？{\r}\NMr.Huang?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.18,1:01:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老鬼德，我把全个房子都搜过了{\r}\NI'm OId Te, I've searched the whole house
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.70,1:01:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}录影带有很多盒{\r}\NThere are many cassettes
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.94,1:01:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}不过没有看到你所说的那一盒{\r}\Nbut not the one you mention
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.82,1:01:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我先回来再说{\r}\NCome back before we take any action
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.46,1:01:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有没有线索？{\r}\NAny cIues?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.10,1:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你先回去休息，这里由我来处理{\r}\NGo back and take a rest. I'll take charge here
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.46,1:01:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官{\r}\NMr.Huang
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.46,1:02:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}阿有，我相信你是无辜的{\r}\NI believe you are innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.54,1:02:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}黄长官，这一次你一定要帮我{\r}\NMr.Huang, you must help me on this
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.78,1:02:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}老鬼德这一件事，除了我知道之外{\r}\NWho else knows the old Te case
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.46,1:02:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有什么人知道？{\r}\Nbesides me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.78,1:02:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}泰利{\r}\NTerry
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.90,1:02:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你明知道泰利这个人这么冲动{\r}\NYou know Terry is impulsive
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.30,1:02:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不单只害死了他，还把你自己也害了{\r}\NNow you've ruined him and yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.50,1:02:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}现在首先要做的就是帮你洗脱嫌疑{\r}\NThe first thing is to prove your innocence
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.30,1:02:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不是说有一盒录影带拷贝吗？带我去拿{\r}\NTake me to get the copy of cassette you mentioned
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.62,1:02:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不相信我？{\r}\NDon't you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.14,1:03:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}信有{\r}\NShun-yu
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.26,1:03:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我昨天录的那一盒带子你有没有看到？{\r}\NHave you seen the cassette I taped yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.50,1:03:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}有，除了德叔之外还有...{\r}\NYes. Besides Te, there's...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.46,1:03:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}还有什么？你快说{\r}\NGo on! Speak up!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.14,1:03:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我不知道，我什么都不知道{\r}\NI don't know, I don't know anything
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.38,1:03:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}究竟知不知道？{\r}\NDo you know or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.78,1:03:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}我什么都不知道{\r}\NI know nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.70,1:03:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}那一盒带子对阿有很重要{\r}\NThe cassette is very important to Yu
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.02,1:03:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}知道在什么地方就马上拿出来{\r}\NBring it if you know where it is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.82,1:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你不用找了，没有{\r}\NThere's no such a cassette
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.90,1:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}一定有的，我昨晚在这一部机过带子的{\r}\NThere must be. I ran it on this VTR recorder last night
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.02,1:03:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你想想有没有拿过出来{\r}\NHave you ever taken it away?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.14,1:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有，我碰也没有碰过{\r}\NNO, I didn't even touch it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.46,1:03:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}你刚才又说有？{\r}\NJust now you said got it
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.78,1:03:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs18}没有那盒带子{\r}\NWithout it
